     In connection with the audit of Advanced Energy's two most recent fiscal years ended December 31, 2003, and the subsequent interim period through the Change Date, there were no disagreements between Advanced Energy and KPMG on any matter of accounting principles or practices, financial statement disclosure, or auditing scope or procedure, which disagreements, if not resolved to KPMG's satisfaction, would have caused KPMG to make reference to the subject matter of the disagreement in connection with its reports.
     None of the reportable events described under Item 304(a)(1)(v) of Regulation S-K occurred within Advanced Energy's two most recent fiscal years or the subsequent interim period through the Change Date.
