     During Advanced Energy's two most recent fiscal years ended December 31, 2003, and the subsequent interim period through the Change Date, neither Advanced Energy nor anyone acting on our behalf consulted with Grant Thornton regarding any of the matters or events set forth in Item 304(a)(2)(i) and (ii) of Regulation S-K.
