          (b) . The Executive shall not be entitled to any of the compensation, benefits or other payments provided herein in respect of the termination of his employment, unless and until he has provided to the Company a full release of claims, substantially in the form of attached hereto, which release shall be dated not earlier than the date of the termination of his employment, which release shall be executed within 30 days of Executive's termination of employment.
