 means, as of the date of determination, the sum of 1) 100% of the aggregate undrawn amount of all outstanding Letters of Credit, plus 1) 100% of the amount of outstanding time drafts accepted by an Underlying Issuer as a result of drawings under Underlying Letters of Credit.
