(j)
    
(1) loans and advances to employees, officers, and directors of Parent or any of its Domestic Subsidiaries for the purpose of purchasing Equity Interests in Parent so long as the proceeds of such loans are used in their entirety to purchase such Equity Interests in Parent, and (1) loans and advances to employees and officers of Parent or any of its Domestic Subsidiaries in the ordinary course of business for any other business purpose and not to exceed (A) $1,000,000 to any one employee and (B) an aggregate amount of $5,000,000 at any one time,
