In the event that the Seller notifies any objections to the Draft P&L Statements and/or the Draft Earn-out Calculation, the Parties shall then attempt to reach an agreement on the treatment of such objections within twenty (20) Business Days from the expiration of the Earn-out Review Period. Any amendments unanimously agreed upon by the Parties shall be incorporated into the Draft P&L Statements and the Draft Earn-out Calculation.
